      <title>新日铁收购案公布后，美国钢铁股飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/nippon-steel-offers-biden-veto-over-us-steel-output-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华盛顿邮报》报道，新日铁公司提出给予美国政府否决权，禁止美国钢铁公司削减产能，以期获得美国总统乔·拜登的批准，收购这家美国标志性公司。美国钢铁公司的股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/nippon-steel-offers-biden-veto-over-us-steel-output-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 19:33:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>圭亚那总统称不会要求埃克森美孚重新谈判合同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/guyana-won-t-ask-exxon-to-renegotiate-contract-president-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[圭亚那总统伊尔凡·阿里周二坚决排除正式要求埃克森美孚公司重新谈判生产合同的可能性，并拒绝了该国政治反对派和活动人士的呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/guyana-won-t-ask-exxon-to-renegotiate-contract-president-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 19:09:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰森食品计划在火灾后分阶段重启佐治亚州肉类加工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/tyson-plans-to-restart-georgia-meat-plant-in-phases-after-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，泰森食品公司计划分阶段重启佐治亚州一家肉类加工厂。该加工厂上周发生火灾，造成一人死亡，数人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/tyson-plans-to-restart-georgia-meat-plant-in-phases-after-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 18:42:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典 Intrum 在美国赢得第 11 章破产计划确认</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/sweden-s-intrum-wins-chapter-11-plan-confirmation-from-us-judge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管遭到少数债权人的反对，一位美国破产法官还是批准了瑞典Intrum AB的债务重组计划，为债务追讨扫清了重大障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/sweden-s-intrum-wins-chapter-11-plan-confirmation-from-us-judge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 18:02:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲将结束通过乌克兰输送俄罗斯天然气的五十年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/russian-gas-flow-to-europe-via-ukraine-set-to-halt-as-time-runs-out-for-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于在一项关键过境协议到期前最后一刻达成解决方案的时间不多，俄罗斯经乌克兰向欧洲输送的天然气似乎即将停止，这使得严重依赖储备的欧洲大陆的能源安全面临更大风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/russian-gas-flow-to-europe-via-ukraine-set-to-halt-as-time-runs-out-for-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 15:19:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储重新考虑降息 推动美元上涨 创九年来最佳年景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/dollar-gains-as-fed-rate-cut-rethink-fuels-best-year-since-2015</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国经济强劲以及当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的减税和关税政策有望维持高利率，美元周二上涨，创下近十年来最强劲的年度涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/dollar-gains-as-fed-rate-cut-rethink-fuels-best-year-since-2015</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 14:54:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易商为供应过剩做准备，油价到 2024 年底涨幅不大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场为明年全球石油过剩做好准备，油价在清淡的假日交易中上涨，2024 年收盘持平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 23:47:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年即将结束，美国股市下跌；美元上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股市的一系列波动持续到今年的最后一个交易日，标志着北美股票投资者原本辉煌的一年以不祥的结局收场。各期限的美国国债收益率保持较高水平，彭博美元现货指数创下 2015 年以来的最大年度涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 22:42:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金有望创 2010 年以来最大涨幅，金属涨跌互现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/gold-s-27-advance-stands-out-in-mixed-year-for-metals-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美国货币宽松政策、持续的地缘政治风险和各国央行的购买潮推动，黄金价格有望创下 14 年来的最大涨幅，其中上涨 27%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/gold-s-27-advance-stands-out-in-mixed-year-for-metals-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 04:09:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普推动的比特币涨势在年底失去动力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/bitcoin-btc-rally-fueled-by-trump-loses-steam-as-year-draws-to-close</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 2024 年接近尾声，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 11 月初获胜所引发的比特币涨势正在停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/bitcoin-btc-rally-fueled-by-trump-loses-steam-as-year-draws-to-close</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 00:17:41 GMT</pubDate>
